Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[seagulls squawking]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--[wings flapping]\N--[squawking continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--[thud]\N--[SAILOR gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"I'm Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Man Who's Gonna Be\NKing of the Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[orchestra playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. My ship\Nis much too sturdy and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,too heavy to be affected by\Nsuch a measly whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN A]\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Would the beautiful\Nlady care to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAILOR B grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ugh. I missed again.\N--[SAILOR A laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike three, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAILOR C]\NI'd be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAILOR B grunts] It's heavier\Nthan I thought it'd be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's filled with beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAILOR A grunts]\NWell, I think it's our beer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not sharing\Nmy half. [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ship off the starboard bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAILORS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[SAILOR C] And they're\Nflying a pirate flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a pirate\Nship in pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--Enemy raid! Enemy raid!\N--[SAILORS scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[cannon fire]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEOPLE screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we've got pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,--[CAPTAIN screams]\N--[PEOPLE screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,People! Please stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Panicking will\Nonly get you hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow my\Ncrew's instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in an orderly fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[explosion]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA]\NFire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA]\NCoby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA] Who is the most\Nbeautiful of all on these seas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh... That would be,\Nthe captain of our ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--Lady Alvida, of course.\N--[ALVIDA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That means a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally gonna\Nsee a little action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So make it count!\NHit 'em with all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--you got, boys!\N--[PIRATES yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEOPLE scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to show them the\Nterror of Iron Club Alvida,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,lady pirate of the seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Coby! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not... real good\Nat this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs] You're telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's 'cause\Nyou're too busy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,backtalking me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Not the club!\NAnything but the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get your ass in gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ALVIDA] Move it, you brat!\N--[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna take\Nyour lives, we swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But we will take everything\Nelse you got on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA] And anyone who fights\Nback'll be eating their dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,off the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NUh, hello...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] I really hope\Nthere's no one in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] That's a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NWow, that's one big barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL grunts, pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATE L growls]\N--[GIRL gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE L]\NHuh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,--I ain't seen you before!\N--[GIRL laughs nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--[GIRL grunts]\N--[PIRATE L screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our favorite coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You trying to hide in here and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,duck out on all\Nthe action again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to haul\Nthis big barrel of beer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,over to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you let us\Nlighten your load?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just startin'\Nto get thirsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alvida will kill us\Nif she ever found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't if you\Nkeep your trap shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs nervously] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucker's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll open her the\Nold fashioned way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[PRATE B yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,slept...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,great...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NWho the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend'll catch\Ncolds sleeping like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES] You're the one\Nwho knocked him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you messing with us\Nwhen you know good and well
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're vicious\Npirates?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,--[gasping]\N--[LUFFY] I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You got any food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls] You damn kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES yell]\N--[COBY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES growl]\NDie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--[metal clinks]\N--[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpers, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C]\NWh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMe? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So... What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Quick!\NYou've got to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If those guys come back\Nhere with their buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,then they'll kill\Nyou on the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that.\NI'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you just blow\Nthis off like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are hundreds\Nof them up on deck
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're waiting for the\Nopportunity to kill anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY grunting]\N--[COBY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY mumbles]\NYou're going the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wait!\N--[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a goldmine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Food! Food! Food! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY laughing]\N--[COBY] Who's knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll be safe in here as\Nlong as no one else gets hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N...box looks promising!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Apples! Excellent! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NUh... Hey! My name's Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Luffy, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty neat when you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,jumped out of that\Nbarrel back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] So are we on\Na pirate ship or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a passenger ship that's\Nbeing raided by pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,pirates under the\Ncommand of Lady Alvida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAw, who cares anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What I wanna know is if\Nthere are any boats on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NI think there are a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Great, 'cause mine got\Nsucked into some big whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NThat one outside? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could have survived that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Yeah! I gotta say,\Nit was a big surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSo are you one of the pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or one of the passangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] It was on a\Nfateful day, long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I stepped out onto\Na small fishing boat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,on the outskirts of town\Nto go catch my dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NTurned out that particular boat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,was actually headed\Nfor a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That was two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] In exchange for\Nthem letting me live,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm forced to live the\Nlife of a cabin boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty stupid,\Nyou know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NGee, thanks for your honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hate it, then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?!\NI can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Nuh-huh! Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the thought of\NAlvida finding me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,scares me so bad,\NI wanna throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing] You're a\Nmoron and a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate people like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY laughs]\N--[COBY sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA] All right, quit your\Nlollygagging around, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta load up everything\Nbefore the Marines get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I catch anyone dawdling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll get a real\Nmouthful of my iron club!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I]\NI love hitting a rich ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J]\NLet's get back to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll break our asses
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if she catches us slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE H]\NOne hit from that club of hers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is enough to have you\Nbeggin' for death! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NThis is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA]\NYeah...? Then out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE M]\NIt came from inside the barrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C]\NSuch a horrible monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA growls]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA grunts]\NWho are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES scream]\N--[PIRATE B groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA]\N...calling a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... we weren't... talkin'...\N'bout... you, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Some guy was hiding in a barrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He could be a bounty hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had the courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I could drift alone in a barrel\Nand be rid of these pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually have my own dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Some day... I'd like to\Nlive out all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So... What about you, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it that first got you\Nto set sail on these seas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--The King?!\N--Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--Are you serious?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But that would mean\Nthat you're a pirate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have one yet,\Nbut I'm lookin' for 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps] King of the Pirates\Nis a title given to one who
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,obtains everything this\Nworld has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the great treasure of\Nwealth, fame, and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasure that you\Nseek is the One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?! That's it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates from all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,are looking for that\Ntreasure, ya know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! It's impossible,\Nimpossible, impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way anyone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,could ever reach the pinnacle\Nduring this great pirate age!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just too many out there\Nthat are meaner and better!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NOw... Why did you hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... I'm used\Nto that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My shipmates smack\Nme around a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...all the time, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this 'cause I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided long ago that I'm\Ngonna be King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to die fighting\Nfor that... then I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that my belly's full,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go get me\Na brand new boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They might even just give me\None if I ask nice enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're generous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I never\Nthought of it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NIf I put my mind to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm prepared to die for it,\Ncould I do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NDo you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I could\Never join the Marines?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMarines?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Catching bad guys is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing I've\Never wanted to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been my dream\Nsince I was a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NThen I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna get stuck here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as a cabin boy for\Nthe rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll break out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll turn right around,\Nand catch Alvida myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA] Who is that you\Nplan on catching, Coby?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you actually think\Nthis twig is gonna help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COBY whimpering]\N--[ALVIDA] Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is that you're\Nnot Zoro, the pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ALVIDA] Coby!\N--[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA] Who is most beautiful\Nof all on these seas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NWell... I... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a sec... I know this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Coby, who's the fat lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let's go.\N--[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATE A yells]\N--[PIRATE A groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE N yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Missed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:16:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE S yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] It's not fair\Nto attack from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE S screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES scream, groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES yelling]\N--[LUFFY screams] And it's even
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES yelling]\N--more not fair to gang
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES yelling]\N--up on a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES groaning]\N--[footseps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NLuffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a rubber man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're... made of rubber...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I... [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So... You've eaten\Nof the Devil Fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I ate the Gum-Gum one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard rumors they existed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd never seen any\Nevidence of them before today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more skilled than\Nthe average deck swabber.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI'm a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA]\NPirate? Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All by yourself\Non these waters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NToday, it's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll find my crew tomorrow\Nor next week or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I need... I dunno,\Nlike ten guys. Yeah, ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA]\NHah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're both pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're not\Nunder the same flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then that would make us enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let's go.\N--But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw how powerful\Nher club is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And of all the villainous\Ncheats in all these waters,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she's easily the most--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to die\Nfighting for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...ugliest thing on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,--[laughing]\N--[COBY] I'm leaving and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna join the Marines!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm gonna spend\Nthe rest of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,beating up dirty\Npirates like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any clue what\Nyou're saying to me right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NOf course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna do what I want,\Nand no one's gonna stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I join the Marines,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna join them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna catch\Nyour lousy ass first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dead, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NNo regrets! No regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I said what I wanted\Nto and fought for my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHeh. That won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI'm rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALVIDA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B] The sky's so\Npretty and blue out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go find a boat and\Ngive it to Coby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's leaving your ship\Nto join the Marines;
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not gonna don't stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NUh... Yeah, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]\NThanks, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NLook! It's the Marines!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Head over there and\Ntell 'em you wanna join.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COBY] Huh?\N--But I'm a pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait! You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I approach them like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll just capture me\Nlike another pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NWe actually managed to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What fun! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're searching for\Nthe elusive One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have to be headed\Nfor the Grand Line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the people\NI've talked to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,call that place the\Npirate graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. And that's why I need\Nan extra-strong crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys mentioned\Nsome pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's he like, Coby?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Last I heard was that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he's being held prisoner\Nat some Marine base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A weakling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're so wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's as violent as a demon,\Nand three times as horrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking\Nabout him anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure if he's good enough,\NI'd ask him to join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] Chasing him down\Nis just plain reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou never know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He might jump at the\Nchance to join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] He's a bad enough guy\Nthat the Marines caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! No no--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,--[thud]\N--Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N'Cause I felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.53,0:23:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.93,0:24:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.27,0:24:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NTell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I untie your ropes,\Nyou join up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.32,0:24:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to team\Nup with a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.94,0:24:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.82,0:24:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody already thinks of\Nyou as an evil bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.16,0:24:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NScrew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.12,0:24:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never done anything\NI regret and I never will!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.45,0:24:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not gonna be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I already decided\Nthat you're joining me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.46,0:24:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Would you stop\Nmaking decisions for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.87,0:24:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.67,0:24:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Enter the Great Swordsman!\NPirate Hunter Roronoa Zoro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.76,0:24:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

